{"tid":708094,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"CY係禮頓既最大靠山？","createTime":"2018-06-19T05:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T09:05:48.000Z","uid":88032,"like":89,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0286783e0290566adf256f7c49a838da663a2ad2","tid":708094,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/132936_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F132936_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=c5d56a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCIMIC經UGL比5千萬CY，然後UGL業務徹出香港，UGL同CY兩者無明顯既利益交割，錢銀成功交收無手尾跟<br />\n<br />\n然後CY係在任期間，不斷推Job比禮頓做，加加埋埋成600億，而且又大又惡，就算出事都可以大大枝野唔使交待<br />\n<br />\n禮頓手握$600億工程　田北辰：大到冇人敢郁佢<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180619/bkn-20180619092602842-0619_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180619%2Fbkn-20180619092602842-0619_00822_001.html&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4cf9967a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180619/bkn-20180619092602842-0619_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nCIMIC呢單買賣認真和味，先利用UGL呢隻白手套過左5000萬數比CY，再摺埋UGL等到賬面上數目乾淨清楚，再等CY坐正果時狂射600億工程比翻禮頓玩，ROI 1200倍<br />\n<br />\n成單Deal合法，錢又袋得穩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/133635_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F133635_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&h=75d7abe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCIMIC股價節節上升，而且最近中國同澳洲又有牙齒印，CIMIC同CY呢D超級中間人，又可以係兩邊左右逢源，互奶油水<br />\n<br />\nChina's Huawei rebuts Australian security concerns<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/video/2018/06/18/chinas-huawei-rebuts-australian-security?videoId=437066229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fvideo%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2Fchinas-huawei-rebuts-australian-security%3FvideoId%3D437066229&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8b7b3ad6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fvideo%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2Fchinas-huawei-rebuts-australian-security%3FvideoId%3D437066229&h=09df01ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/video/2018/06/18/chinas-huawei-rebuts-australian-security?videoId=437066229</a><br />\n<br />\nCY黎緊仲會做埋超級大灣區區長，到時候D工程量必定會大到不得之了，CIMIC又坐定粒六奶埋呢堆超級工程，但到果時未必用禮頓字頭，可能係：<br />\n<br />\n- CPB<br />\n- THIESS<br />\n- SEDGMAN<br />\n- PACIFIC PARTNERSHIPS<br />\n- EIC ACTIVITIES<br />\n- VENTIA<br />\n- BIC<br />\n<br />\nCIMIC無限風光，假若各位身上有D澳紙，不仿買些少CIMIC坐坐<br />\n<br />\n買CIMIC = 買CY<br />\n<br />\nCY風光幾耐，CIMIC就風光幾耐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f235b02cd5372cd924da6f5334817743db4e53b7","tid":708094,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6b0bfea3a9f2c260bbfc898a297bdf6da6bcc6","tid":708094,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"推 不錯推論"},{"pid":"a21dff5d4bed1576bb1b05f64e6192ef9689a012","tid":708094,"uid":88032,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bf6b0bfea3a9f2c260bbfc898a297bdf6da6bcc6","tid":708094,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"推 不錯推論"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"CIMIC一定買得過<br />\n<br />\nICAC都查唔到，可想而知佢背後既後台幾硬<br />\n<br />\n習大大話：打鐵還需自身硬<br />\n<br />\n咁Q硬，唔係唔掃呀！"},{"pid":"bbc1e99b351d7b11510c6f0c1e3aa5791c6d8249","tid":708094,"uid":143621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T0