成收購過程入面既其中一個Hidden Agenda？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"或者我再補充<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻，無人可以絕對證明：<br />\n<br />\nCY &lt; &gt; UGL &lt; &gt; CIMIC<br />\n<br />\n之間有確實既利益往來，因為就咁睇水面盤數，已經亂到九彩，枱底既野就更加無可能Black &amp; White<br />\n<br />\n要證明佢地之間真係無直接利害關係，只能夠用今次政府對待禮頓既取態，去見微之著<br />\n<br />\n假若禮頓今次都係可以安然渡過，而CIMIC旗下既其它字號又繼續接基建大單既話，咁就可以確立CIMIC既後台真係好硬，而其後台係CY既可能性真係好高<br />\n<br />\n假若政府今次係決心煮死禮頓，而CIMIC旗下既其它字號未來都無乜點接到基建大單既話，就當我鳩Up，吹水，我錯"},{"pid":"842b65e9a2f3e433014ff8319e1365deaaefde16","tid":708094,"uid":49544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053a70d0cc2190ebd78bf2c754362d3808203281","tid":708094,"uid":179283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"ICAC訓撚左?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"詐訓既人永遠叫唔醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604ecef6121cc2dc16322c51d61e376a801767dd","tid":708094,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842b65e9a2f3e433014ff8319e1365deaaefde16","tid":708094,"uid":49544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053a70d0cc2190ebd78bf2c754362d3808203281","tid":708094,"uid":179283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"ICAC訓撚左?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"詐訓既人永遠叫唔醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:27:06.000Z","msg":"站在ICAC立場，好難查<br />\n<br />\n一跨境，數就亂，就難查<br />\n<br />\nFBI都搞唔掂"},{"pid":"d2092001b08a7adbb45caa0e634e9bf9c3f0fada","tid":708094,"uid":59863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"香港Civil  咪得金門 禮頓  法國佬 有機 有經驗做開 <br />\n其次已經是中國佬果堆垃圾<br />\n是諗唔到禮頓D監管  差左咁多"},{"pid":"9db60e3788829f4d3df4b5f54c3c7fa381e29216","tid":708094,"uid":59863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"604ecef6121cc2dc16322c51d61e376a801767dd","tid":708094,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q